item.title: The TLA Fan Breakdown: Baseball Edition | The Lady Athlete- No Frills Athletics
item.description:
The TLA Fan Breakdown: Baseball Edition | The Lady Athlete- No Frills Athletics

With each new professional sports season comes the opportunity to people watch at the ballpark, on people's Instagram posts, or at whatever sports bar you're at. There is no denying that within the male or female category, there are different levels of fandom. Denying it only pushes you further into one of those categories.
